CHAT WIDGET DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------

The chat widget at /chat/ calls third-party APIs (Anthropic or
OpenAI) using API keys the user supplies themselves. The author
and this repository do not receive, store, or process any user
API keys. Use of those APIs is governed by the respective
provider's terms of service.

